Nector

FAQ:


What is Nector?

Nector is a social networking app/website



What is the purpose?

The goal of nector in the simplest terms is to connect people(conNECTOR), with themselves, with others, with the world around them, etc



How does it compare with other social apps?

Right now nector is like your personal contacts on your phone except more information and a more in depth profile can be created, and these contacts can be more easily pooled and shared with other friends. Helping you organize the friends you have and also meet new friends
